01:04.328 --> 01:05.578
DANNY: Oh, hey, Simon.

01:05.580 --> 01:07.329
You finally come back to say good-bye?

01:07.551 --> 01:09.331
Hey, Simple Simon,

01:09.333 --> 01:11.500
stop ogling over the help
and bring me over my grub.

01:11.502 --> 01:13.182
