01:16.174 --> 01:17.673
Uh, good. You know?

01:17.675 --> 01:18.841
Just workin'.

01:19.938 --> 01:21.886
Uh, I'm in a bit of a hurry, actually,

01:21.888 --> 01:23.275
so...

01:24.276 --> 01:26.182
I'll walk you out.

01:26.184 --> 01:28.601
Quite a career path he's on.

01:28.603 --> 01:32.354
From trial science technician
to bike messenger.

01:32.356 --> 01:34.523
(SIGHS)

01:37.253 --> 01:39.411
(SIGHS) Well, that was weird.

01:39.413 --> 01:41.363
You know what's weird?

01:41.365 --> 01:43.582
A guy working somewhere for four months

01:43.584 --> 01:46.118
and then suddenly just not showing up.

01:46.465 --> 01:47.920
You know what else is weird?

01:47.922 --> 01:50.172
Uh, somebody dating somebody

01:50.174 --> 01:53.626
and then, all of a sudden, they're gone.

01:53.628 --> 01:54.960
They've moved.

01:54.962 --> 01:56.128
Changed their number.

01:56.130 --> 01:57.296
Don't show up for work.

01:57.298 --> 01:58.848
E-mails bounce back.

01:59.186 --> 02:00.883
I'm sorry.

02:01.605 --> 02:03.352
I hope you weren't worried.

02:03.354 --> 02:04.553
Following people online

02:04.555 --> 02:06.055
when they don't want to be followed,

02:06.057 --> 02:08.023
that's what I do.

02:11.657 --> 02:14.063
Three and a half weeks
is kind of a long time

02:14.065 --> 02:16.115
to not text somebody that you care about.

02:16.117 --> 02:17.449
(ELEVATOR BELL CHIMES)

02:17.451 --> 02:19.652
(DOORS OPEN)

02:20.404 --> 02:22.488
I know I-I owe you an explanation,

02:22.490 --> 02:26.458
but... I'm trying to get
this $30 bonus and, uh...

02:26.460 --> 02:28.077
$30.

02:28.590 --> 02:31.330
Cool. Well, don't let me waste
another second of your time.

02:31.332 --> 02:33.332
You can just have a nice life, Simon.

02:33.334 --> 02:37.636
By the way, you look like hell.

02:37.638 --> 02:39.972
Your eyes are bloodshot,
and your hands are shaking.

02:39.974 --> 02:43.475
Whatever you're doing, really...

02:43.477 --> 02:46.095
keep it up. (ELEVATOR BELL CHIMES)

02:46.097 --> 02:48.097
I'm sorry, Cable.

02:48.816 --> 02:51.767
